'''Pool''' was a recreational pocket billiards game played on [[Planet/Legends|worlds]] across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. [[Deacon]] and [[Windy Starkiller|Windy]] were known to play computer-assisted pool games in [[Tosche Station/Legends|Tosche Station]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

